<div class="page">
 <div class="header">
    <h2 class="header_text"> Grandma's Secret Apple Pie </h2>
 </div>
<br>
<br>
 <div class="body">
    <p>The apple pie recipe has been in my family for generations and never fails to delight</p>
 </div>
<br>
<br>
<div class="body">
    <h2>Ingrediants</h2>
    <ul> 
        <li> 1/2 cup sugar</li>
        <li> 2 tsp ground cinnamon</li>
        <li> 6 medium-sized apples , peeled and sliced </li>
    </ul>
 </div>

 <br>
<br>
<div class="body">
    <h2>Instructions</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).</li>
        <li>In a bowl, mix the sugar and cinnamon.</li>
        <li>Toss the apples in the sugar-cinnamon mixture.</li>
    </ol>
 </div>
